  <tr><td>Staging Folder</td><td>C:\Users\john.slagboom\Desktop\Git\data\new\</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Update Script</td><td>bash update-data.sh from C:\Users\john.slagboom\Desktop\Git\ in Git Bash (merge, sanitize, push, clear staging)</td></tr>
